  <h2>Using <code>&lt;mark&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;code&gt;</code> tags</h2>

  <p>This is a normal paragraph with a <mark>highlighted text</mark> using <code>&lt;mark&gt;</code>.</p>

  <p>Here is an example of inline code: <code>console.log("Hello World");</code></p>

  <p>You can combine them: <mark><code>let x = 10;</code></mark></p>

